  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare cold snare polypectomy and conventional polypectomy for
      the removal and retrieval of small colorectal polyps.

      Cold snare polypectomy for colorectal polyps up to 8 mm is expected to be more effective than
      conventional polypectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
